  <title>IC-4 Sample Outcomes</title>
  <introduction>
    <p>For the quiz on this outcome you would be given 40 minutes to complete 1 problem 
        with parts. For these you will be asked to set up all three problems but only 
        asked to fully evaluate one. Here are samples of the types of problems you will encounter:</p>
  </introduction>
